{"tid":136293,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"伊巴謙稱冠軍非一人功勞「獎盃已袋」懶理批評","createTime":"2017-02-27T03:12:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T05:30:49.000Z","uid":60256,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81bc1971ba79c4fa0770b682e129be707f2237d9","tid":136293,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T03:12:04.000Z","msg":"在5項賽事都有入球的伊巴謙莫域（Zlatan Ibrahimovic）於聯賽盃5戰入4球，他仍否認是一人的功勞︰「一如我所料，我加盟是要證明自己及勝利，這是團隊的勝利，不單是我個人。」被問到修咸頓的整體表現更勝一籌，他表示︰「這不重要，獎盃已袋回家（It doesn't matter, I bring the trophy home）。他們做得很好才得以連追兩球，但我們取得奠定勝局一球。曼聯不是踢出100%，但人們只會記得誰是贏家，而不是踢得較好一隊。」<br />\n<br />\n黑哨都可以咁串<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ee738b08be5f4096067f1af5ef63ff128a99b5","tid":136293,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T03:12:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b728213f4b76ef1d16e33529e3b15fedae6d53","tid":136293,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T03:13:23.000Z","msg":"有冠軍梗係有得吋<br />\n唔通好似有啲冇冠都仲要吋柒柒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3facadd3d90484ca22cf21fce78a5765a8374e1","tid":136293,"uid":33441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T03:13:53.000Z","msg":"但人們只會記得誰是贏家，而不是踢得較好一隊<br />\n呢句真，抵佢咁串<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b42096d85c38763bf929300c0a2b547e38a947b8","tid":136293,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T03:18:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冠軍梗係有得吋<br />\n唔通好似有啲冇冠都仲要吋柒柒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n辣殺黑哨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d228f3c63e17a9f44a98736e6007542e5dff87","tid":136293,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:49:12.000Z","msg":"靠黑哨的冠軍，可恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm